msgctxt "an10.101:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.101:0.2"
msgid "11. Samaṇasaññāvagga "
msgstr "11. Perceptions for Ascetics "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.101:0.3"
msgid "101. Samaṇasaññāsutta "
msgstr "101. Perceptions for Ascetics "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.101:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, samaṇasaññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when these three perceptions for ascetics are developed and cultivated they fulfill seven things. "

msgctxt "an10.101:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an10.101:1.3"
msgid "Vevaṇṇiyamhi ajjhupagato, parapaṭibaddhā me jīvikā, añño me ākappo karaṇīyoti—"
msgstr "‘I have secured freedom from class.’ ‘My livelihood is tied up with others.’ ‘My behavior should be different.’ "

msgctxt "an10.101:1.4"
msgid "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso samaṇasaññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti. "
msgstr "When these three perceptions for ascetics are developed and cultivated they fulfill seven things. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.211, sc2
msgctxt "an10.101:2.1"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

#. VAR: Santatakārī → niccaṃ santatakārī (bj) | satatakārī (s1-3, pts1, mr)
#. VAR: santatavutti → satatavuttī (s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: āraddhavīriyo ca → āraddhaviriyo ca (bj, pts1) | āraddhaviriyo (s1-3)
msgctxt "an10.101:2.2"
msgid "Santatakārī hoti santatavutti sīlesu, anabhijjhālu hoti, abyāpajjo hoti, anatimānī hoti, sikkhākāmo hoti, “idamatthan”tissa hoti jīvitaparikkhāresu, āraddhavīriyo ca viharati. "
msgstr "Their deeds and behavior are always consistent with the precepts. They’re content, kind-hearted, and humble. They want to train. They use the necessities of life after reflecting on their purpose. They’re energetic. "

msgctxt "an10.101:2.3"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso samaṇasaññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ime satta dhamme paripūrentī”ti. "
msgstr "When those three perceptions for ascetics are developed and cultivated they fulfill these seven things.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.101:2.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

